snippet.title: PlayStation Experience 2015: Battlefront - Best of Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Learn more: http://starwars.ea.com/battlefront
Watch the best moments from the Star Wars Battlefront community. Let’s Play Star Wars!

Star Wars™ Battlefront™ is available now on PS4.
 
Taking place in the aftermath of the Rebel victory in the Battle of Endor, players will experience the events that created the massive, battle-scarred landscape of Jakku shown in Star Wars™: The Force Awakens™.

Star Wars™ Battlefront™ The Battle of Jakku is available for free to all players December 8th on PS4.
 
Subscribe and be the first to see more trailers and gameplay: http://bit.ly/1Ge7NQ1 

www.StarWarsBattlefront.com
